                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirement</strong> The totenmaske hit the same enemy with two claw Strikes this turn and is still adjacent to it</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The totenmaske drains flesh from the creature's body. The creature becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 2} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 1} unless it succeeds at a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:25] save (@Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 2} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 2} on a critical failure).</p>"
